    ISourceLocation, IInitializableDefinitionNode, IASNode, IDefinitionNode, IDocumentableDefinitionNode, ITypedNode, IVariableNode

    public class ConfigConstNode
extends VariableNode
    A ConfigConstNode is a conditional compilation const that only exists at compile time. It's value is computed while parsing is taking place and it is replaced with the literal value it signifies.
